---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="Smart TV vs Android Box - EXYU IPTV" description="Detaljna usporedba Smart TV i Android Box uređaja za gledanje IPTV sadržaja.">
  <section class="section bg-white">
    <div class="container-custom">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        <a href="/blog" class="text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-700 mb-6 inline-flex items-center gap-1"><svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M15 19l-7-7 7-7"/></svg>Natrag na blog</a>
        <span class="bg-blue-100 text-blue-700 px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm font-medium">Usporedba</span>
        <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-slate-800 mt-4 mb-6">Smart TV naspram Android Box - Šta je bolje?</h1>
        <div class="flex items-center gap-4 text-slate-500 mb-8"><span>24.02.2025</span><span>•</span><span>6 min čitanja</span></div>
        <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
          <p class="text-xl text-slate-600 mb-8">Koji uređaj odabrati za gledanje IPTV-a? Usporedili smo Smart TV i Android Box.</p>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-800 mt-12 mb-4">Smart TV prednosti</h2>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 text-slate-600 mb-8">
            <li>Jednostavno korištenje</li>
            <li>Nema dodatnih uređaja</li>
            <li>Direktna integracija</li>
          </ul>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-800 mt-12 mb-4">Android Box prednosti</h2>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 text-slate-600 mb-8">
            <li>Više aplikacija</li>
            <li>Bolje performanse</li>
            <li>Jeftinije opcije</li>
          </ul>
          <div class="bg-blue-50 rounded-2xl p-8 mt-8">
            <a href="/kontakt" class="btn btn-primary">Pitajte za savjet</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
